@booksApi = https://localhost:51491
@bookCoversApi = https://localhost:52644

### Get all books (controller)
GET {{booksApi}}/api/books

### Get a single book (controller)
GET {{booksApi}}/api/books/5b1c2b4d-48c7-402a-80c3-cc796ad49c6b

### Get all books (Minimal API)
GET {{booksApi}}/api/minimal/books

### Get a single book (Minimal API)
GET {{booksApi}}/api/minimal/books/5b1c2b4d-48c7-402a-80c3-cc796ad49c6b

### Create a book
POST {{booksApi}}/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "authorId": "24810dfc-2d94-4cc7-aab5-cdf98b83f0c9",
  "title": "The Cold Six Thousand",
  "description": "The Cold Six Thousand is the first sequel to American Tabloid."
}

### Stream books (controller) — watch items arrive one by one
GET {{booksApi}}/api/booksstream

### Stream books (Minimal API)
GET {{booksApi}}/api/minimal/booksstream

### Get a single book cover from the BookCovers API directly
GET {{bookCoversApi}}/api/bookcovers/test-dummycover1

### Get a single book cover — with fault simulation
GET {{bookCoversApi}}/api/bookcovers/test-dummycover1?returnFault=true

### Get book covers via Books API (sequential vs concurrent — switch in code)
GET {{booksApi}}/api/books/5b1c2b4d-48c7-402a-80c3-cc796ad49c6b/bookcovers

### Get a book with covers (combined response)
GET {{booksApi}}/api/books/5b1c2b4d-48c7-402a-80c3-cc796ad49c6b

### Get books — purely synchronous (baseline)
GET {{booksApi}}/api/books/sync

### Get books — sync-over-async BAD CODE (.Result)
GET {{booksApi}}/api/books/syncoverasync
